Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从圣天界拿到神圣松明回到第五星界的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了用黑夜乌鸦消灭镇上光明的大督领
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次向光之女神像进发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,在这时候!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落入魔界之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三十八话\N再见 武一郎师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人盯上了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家先去暗黑镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟也绽·奥里零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡不是已向光之女神像去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是,正如你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么正如你所说?你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之女神像点燃了松明之火的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掌管的第五星界也会被渡他们抢去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心吧,魔界三兄弟的各位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算说他们有松明之火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能这么简单可以接近光之女神像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有办法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一把松明之火做也做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲到这里面吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃啊!逃啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知它们何时会破门而入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一个到屋顶!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子第一!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个便是光之女神像?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要燃点起那松明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能令第五星界恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能对抗的数量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把鱼叉投到那建筑物处吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到还是做不到?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是做得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小事只不过是早餐前的运动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐前的意思便是昨天的晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,试试吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了那大厦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能登上女神像了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的要去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在这时候黑暗的世界还在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要冷静啊,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我出了冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命也缩短了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本领呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黑暗猎人玛达莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了令渡变成魔界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第七星界而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令渡变成魔界的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你迟早会知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身边已布满了黑暗之绿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一碰上便会分成两半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是这个第五星界的波士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟也绽·奥里零
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地把松明交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会交给你这样的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要丢下去了呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个样子什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GoodLuck,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟摇来摇去地避开!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟会对无还手之力的人出手,太卑鄙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘飘攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些小把戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢铁兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松明会熄掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松明没有事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这火炎是加麾斯利路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们的神圣火炎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会因那样的攻击熄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的渡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这伟大加美昂把你送进地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是刚才那家伙的魔神吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,小心了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让你去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双重车胎攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,谢谢你!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊,松明有危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火不能熄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便压碎它!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一名!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好 火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟也绽·奥里零!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,不要输!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形,加美昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双重车胎攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去渡很危险的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔…要电话的那边有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我布下的陷阱味道怎样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里杀掉你虽然很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但首先我要先收拾目标物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后才慢慢再和你交手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还有命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以…让你成功吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是时候解决你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战神丸,现在登场!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大加美昂的真正力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是这样的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超飞龙拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有效!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从里面攻击,但外面却攻击不到里面的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟用卑鄙的方法!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上…渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞上去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形,飞龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙光击拳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,伟也绽没有另到钢掌!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:16:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样剩下的只差一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶得及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是渡他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体却动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,觉悟吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:17:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,我点火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,振作点啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…星界山拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔,振作点啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快离开!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:19:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武一郎老师已不是我们的同伴了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师他…武一郎老师他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成魔界的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟说师傅变成了魔界的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有这样的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武一郎老师并不是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面时…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即将出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着光线还没有消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着明天的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的彩虹彼岸里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了两个人未来的风

